      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not that simple though. counselors just tell you to \"budget\" and \"make a plan,\" but the math literally doesn't work. the interest alone is more than i make. it's like looking at a wall that's just getting thicker every day. i feel like i'm just wasting everyone's time even being alive when i'm just a black hole of money and stress. even my family... they're just waiting for the other shoe to drop. i feel like a burden that won't go away.",
